@startuml Model Training Pipeline Flowchart
start
:Load Data (pandas reads health_data.csv);
:Preprocess Data\n- Handle missing values\n- Encode categorical variables;
:Select Features & Target\n- Symptoms, vitals, demographics\n- Target: diagnosis (default);
:Split Data (train_test_split 80/20);
:Train Model (RandomForestClassifier);
:Evaluate Model (classification_report);
:Show Validation Metrics\n- Accuracy\n- Precision\n- Recall\n- F1-score;
:Save Model (joblib to model.pkl);
stop
@enduml
